modName: Ronnie James Dio preset for Racemenu
summary: A Racemenu Preset to turn your Wood-Elf character into Ronnie James Dio.
descriptionHtml:
A racemenu preset for to made your Bosmer/Wood-Elf character into Ronnie James Dio.

[center][youtube]YNb_SSE-jVc[/youtube]
[/center]Hard Requirements:

[url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE. [/url]

[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624]Racemenu.[/url]

[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168]Apachiiskyhair. [/url]

[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722]The Eyes of Beauty[/url] (almost a soft requirement, as it's not going to crash or look radically different to you load the preset without it. You'll just have to choose a different eye-color).


Soft Requirements:

[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2356]Xenius Character Enhancement[/url] (for the skin and face textures).

[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/91066]Salt and Wind - Rough Hair for Apachii Sky Hair[/url] (the hair texture I use).

[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/63839]I Can't Believe it's Not ENB 3[/url] (it's what I use instead of an ENB I don't know why I put this here. I mean, everybody mentions what ENB they are using on the pages for their Racemenu presets).
author: ArgonianSoldier
